---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="下载">

  <style>
    .dl-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 18px;
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .dl-card {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 36px 32px;
    }
    .dl-card.full { grid-column: span 2; }
    .dl-card .platform-label {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .dl-card .platform-label.docker { background: rgba(60,252,140,0.1); color: var(--green); }
    .dl-card .platform-label.win { background: rgba(96,165,250,0.1); color: var(--blue); }
    .dl-card .platform-label.mac { background: rgba(167,139,250,0.1); color: var(--purple); }
    .dl-card .platform-label.src { background: rgba(240,160,48,0.1); color: var(--amber); }

    .dl-card h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .dl-card .meta { color: var(--text-quiet); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .dl-card pre {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px 18px; margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.65; overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .dl-card pre code { font-family: 'Fira Code', 'Cascadia Code', monospace; color: var(--text-dim); }
    .dl-card .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .dl-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .dl-card.full { grid-column: span 1; }
    }
  </style>

  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>下载 AI Privacy Gateway</h1>
    <p>选择你的平台，30 秒开始保护 AI 数据隐私</p>
  </div>

  <section style="padding-top:10px">
    <div class="dl-grid">
      <div class="dl-card full">
        <span class="platform-label docker">推荐</span>
        <h3>Docker</h3>
        <p class="meta">Linux / macOS / Windows — 一键部署</p>
        <pre><code>docker run -d \
  -p 9999:9999 \
  -v ./vault_data:/app/vault_data \
  ghcr.io/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway:lite</code></pre>
        <a href="/docs/deploy" class="btn btn-outline">部署文档</a>
      </div>

      <div class="dl-card">
        <span class="platform-label win">Windows</span>
        <h3>Windows</h3>
        <p class="meta">单文件 .exe · Windows 10 / 11</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway/releases" class="btn btn-primary">前往下载</a>
      </div>

      <div class="dl-card">
        <span class="platform-label mac">macOS</span>
        <h3>macOS</h3>
        <p class="meta">单文件可执行 · macOS 12+</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway/releases" class="btn btn-primary">前往下载</a>
      </div>

      <div class="dl-card full">
        <span class="platform-label src">源码</span>
        <h3>Python 源码</h3>
        <p class="meta">pip 安装 · Python 3.11+</p>
        <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway
cd ai-privacy-gateway
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py</code></pre>
        <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="faq-list" style="max-width:900px">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>1. 验证运行</h4>
        <p>打开浏览器访问 <code>http://localhost:9999/health</code>，看到 <code>{'{'}"status":"healthy"{'}'}</code> 即成功。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>2. 配置 AI 客户端</h4>
        <p>将 API 地址从 <code>https://api.openai.com</code> 改为 <code>http://localhost:9999</code>，API Key 不变。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>3. 查看管理后台</h4>
        <p>访问 <code>http://localhost:9999/admin</code> 查看拦截统计和脱敏日志。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
